  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0da2\u0dd2\u0dbb \u0dad\u0dc0 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Vajira makes another prophecy",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "United National Party Chairman Mr. Vajira Abeywardena says that Ranil Wickremesinghe will get 140 votes or more in the parliamentary election to select the President.",
        "Mr. Abeywardena, who said that none of his previous predictions were wrong, also said that \"Ranil\" is 1000 percent \"sure\" that he will be the president.",
        "Mr. Abeywardena said that as the chairman of the United National Party, he has discussed the matters necessary to free the country from anarchy with Pohottuwa and other members of the party.",
        "The UNP chairman also said that if all 225 members of the parliament work together, the country can be freed from anarchy. Mr. Vajira Abeywardena said that the democratic struggle, which was also approved by the United National Party, had gone to a point where the flames would ignite and if the process of burning down the houses of the people's representatives and destroying the state property continued, the country would be completely destroyed.",
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe is the only leader who has clearly presented a program at a time of crisis when no one has clearly presented a series of policies that will take the country forward, said Mr. Vajira Abiveardhana."
      ],
